Puppet module: datacenter

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages datacenter software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include datacenter              # Install and run datacenter with standard configurations.
include datacenter::disable     # Disable datacenter service.
include datacenter::disableboot # Disable datacenter service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include datacenter::absent      # Remove datacenter package.

DEPENDENCIES:
